title: That Metal Show S11E06 Sammy Hagar, Michael Anthony.mkv
description: Sammy Hagar co-hosts That Metal Show with Eddie Trunk, Jim Florentine and Don Jamieson. That means tequila shots for all. Sammy's long time bandmate then joins to discuss his uneasy departure from Van Halen and his current project, Chickenfoot. And don't miss this week's surprise guest for Eddie's birthday celebration. Guest guitarist John 5 returns.
